premise_source_doc_sentence: Michael Joseph Jackson  (  August 29 , 1958 -- June 25 , 2009  )  was an American singer , songwriter , record producer , dancer , actor , and philanthropist .
In May 2009 , Payne started to work with Michael Jackson and Kenny Ortega on This Is It which was a sold-out series of fifty concerts by Jackson to be held at The O2 Arena in London .
Released by MJJ Music on October 26 , 2009 , This Is It features previously released music , as well as six previously unreleased recordings by Michael Jackson .
